ily joshy woshy: Chewing Clock Rules The chewing clock rules are as follows: - You must chew clock if you have a 33+ point lead at any point in the game. - You must chew clock if you have a 25+ point lead at any point in the 2nd half. - You may chew clock up 10+ points in the 4th quarter with 4 minutes or less of gameplay. Any person chewing clock outside of these parameters will be subject to punishment.
